{"tid":597471,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"急~誠意地想問下有無後天食物敏感呢回事？","createTime":"2018-03-18T16:11:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T19:05:06.000Z","uid":92376,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c517ef3c5ebeb650189d80ed2cb70df9b8678204","tid":597471,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:11:26.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n最近發現自己右手成日起粒粒紅晒好痕<br />\n觀察左大約半個月至一個月時間<br />\n似乎係蝦作怪，因為有時係食完m記痕，有時就係夜晚果餐有雪蝦會痕<br />\n但我由細到大都唔對蝦敏感<br />\n所以想向大家請教有無後天食物敏感呢回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38060a604bd31d078640bdd707c0916af2d518d9","tid":597471,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":13,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:12:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"15788b181cf8044f7303810de8ddfa2e0eb83b29","tid":597471,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:16:47.000Z","msg":"可能係你細個冇留意又或者唔明顯姐"},{"pid":"3772302d88498ffab44bad81796350d0514f4977","tid":597471,"uid":55002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:18:37.000Z","msg":"係濕熱，睇中醫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c637f9a4712a50e405482691c26bdf79fe5d522","tid":597471,"uid":42407,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:21:16.000Z","msg":"信我，你之後會周身病痛，我之前都係咁，而家成日出出入入醫院"},{"pid":"04343541bf124ecf9a2405cb5fa11b18795de177","tid":597471,"uid":26084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:32:43.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"71cf2e264cacb54d5cb3d75131ea67390028a54e","tid":597471,"uid":83961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:34:36.000Z","msg":"話後天食物敏感，不如話係你咁多年以黎食某類野太多，搞到身體積埋太多毒素先有咁既問題<br />\n<br />\n試下搵一排食清淡D，睇下中醫執兩劑排下毒，到時再食番同類野應該唔會有事"},{"pid":"84540b15c2df7e8cc450f82abff6a30d64b19d7c","tid":597471,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:37:23.000Z","msg":"影黎睇下如果唔係肉酸的話"},{"pid":"32f2edb062714c4aa9280ba072e1a0a45fc7d8eb","tid":597471,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84540b15c2df7e8cc450f82abff6a30d64b19d7c","tid":597471,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:37:23.000Z","msg":"影黎睇下如果唔係肉酸的話"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:45:02.000Z","msg":"已經散左，下次先"},{"pid":"c82a73e1a4bc2458f73792da06c7cf5ed06effc9","tid":597471,"uid":45442,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:47:28.000Z","msg":"有，我都係細個可以食蝦，大個一食就皮膚紅腫/口腫面腫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d9b0bf221507104ea2afc1cf4cc9ca3e9804b12","tid":597471,"uid":155344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:50:31.000Z","msg":"我都係後天食物敏感<br />\n嚴重個時成身都會出風癩 腫起一舊舊<br />\n日日都係咁 諗起都想死<br />\n但係我由細到大都冇試過敏感<br />\n係突然間身體有呢種反應<br />\n睇過好多次醫生 都唔知原因"},{"pid":"3728320c27bc9cefb5c5cd14e71ca83c542980b8","tid":597471,"uid":111398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:50:42.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n細個食蝦蟹乜事都冇，大個左會嘴腫/喉嚨腫或者痕咁，生蝦仲嚴重個喉嚨比刀割咁差啲抖唔到氣"},{"pid":"4c1a6c9f47d03dc0fc16951a360cd0fd25ddd2de","tid":597471,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84540b15c2df7e8cc450f82abff6a30d64b19d7c","tid":597471,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:37:23.000Z","msg":"影黎睇下如果唔係肉酸的話"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T07:32:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25196dd2b847e1487e061db3bb5223b56148908a","tid":597471,"uid":56906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T09:17:48.000Z","msg":"有冇挑蝦腸?<br />\n<br />\n利申: 試過敏感因為蝦腸, 蝦肉冇事"},{"pid":"caab493dd4a28b08e9a87a9318d3bc2e61575ab6","tid":597471,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T09:38:36.000Z","msg":"同你症狀一樣，自從中學出現敏感之後以後都斷唔到尾"},{"pid":"2ee3247d5ebac5575aae7a83d6107f4431931947","tid":597471,"uid":100912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T09:44:16.000Z","msg":"我都試過呀<br />\n嗰排壓力大，只要食蝦就敏感<br />\n轉咗工就咩事都冇lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c87977d743cfd692226a22c40232cec1136610d4","tid":597471,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T15:37:48.000Z","msg":"建議你快啲去做個血液檢驗"},{"pid":"a697a7cbd4271a86d1bc026929ab2a65a88d8aa6","tid":597471,"uid":124941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T19:05:06.000Z","msg":"咪又係天生只不過未發出嚟"}]}